OL,6,FWorkers are being "cheated" out of
OL,7,Fholiday pay worth #2 billion as some
OL,8,Femployers deliberately deny holiday
OL,9,Frequests, according to a new report.
OL,11,FThe TUC said its research suggested
OL,12,Fthat 1.1 million employees did not
OL,13,Ftake any of the paid holiday they were
OL,14,Fentitled to last year.
