OL,3,CSome employers deliberately rejecting
OL,4,Cworker holiday requests, report says
OL,6,FAmong the main reasons included were a
OL,7,Fculture where workers feared asking
OL,8,Ffor paid time off could lead to them
OL,9,Fbeing treated unfavourably, staff
OL,10,Fstruggling with unrealistic workloads
OL,11,Fthat did not allow time to take leave,
OL,12,Fas well as requests being turned down,
OL,13,Fsaid the TUC.
OL,15,FThe report, published to mark the
OL,16,Fbeginning of the TUC's annual Congress
OL,17,Fon Sunday, said the "missing weeks" of
OL,18,Fholiday paid added up to #1,800 per
OL,19,Faffected employee.
