OL,3,CSome employers deliberately rejecting
OL,4,Cworker holiday requests, report says
OL,6,FThe jobs with the highest numbers of
OL,7,Fstaff losing out were waiters and
OL,8,Fwaitresses (59,000), care workers and
OL,9,Fhome carers (55,000), and kitchen and
OL,10,Fcatering assistants (50,000), showing
OL,11,Fthat low paid workers were most at
OL,12,Frisk of losing paid holiday
OL,13,Fentitlement, said the report.
OL,15,FMillions of workers were missing out
OL,16,Fon many other basic employment rights
OL,17,Fdue to a lack of enforcement, the TUC
OL,18,Fadded.
