OL,6,FIt is calling for effective
OL,7,Fenforcement of employment rights to
OL,8,Fhelp workers, as well as decent
OL,9,Femployers who were being "undercut" by
OL,10,Fthose ignoring their legal duties.
OL,12,FThe TUC is supporting Labour's plans
OL,13,Ffor a Fair Work Agency and has accused
OL,14,Fthe previous Conservative government
OL,15,Fof allowing bad employers to cheat
OL,16,Fstaff out of basic workplace rights.
