OL,3,CSome employers deliberately rejecting
OL,4,Cworker holiday requests, report says
OL,6,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said:
OL,7,F"We all deserve a break from work to
OL,8,Fspend time off with our friends and
OL,9,Ffamily, but more than a million
OL,10,Fworking people have been deprived of
OL,11,Fany of the paid leave they are due,
OL,12,Fand hundreds of thousands more have
OL,13,Fbeen denied basic rights like being
OL,14,Fpaid the minimum wage.
OL,16,F"The Conservative government sat back
OL,17,Fand let bad employers cheat their
OL,18,Fstaff out of their basic workplace
OL,19,Frights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
